title: The Only Hole In Your Performance That Can Utterly Destroy Your Success, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO293
itunes:title: The Only Hole In Your Performance That Can Utterly Destroy Your Success, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO293
description: There’s a lot of you guys out there who think you can tolerate a little compromise or deviation in your performance or integrity…what I call “a hole in your bucket”…& still succeed. The reality is, some of the giants of history have been reduced to f*cking ruins because they allowed a hole in their bucket. What was it?…why is it so lethal?…& most important, how do you protect yourself from it? Take a listen & find out.
